            "title": "北角半山煙花海景兩房1,367萬易手 超長情業主袋1,359萬勁賺179倍",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Gi6urHZC.6momx3URoSl_g--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/vi/28hse_com_210/86924ce5bc523d40dffec00eb8acb236\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure></div>",
